{"ec":"ET00040648","t":"The Jungle Book","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/the-jungle-book-et00040648-08-10-2016-03-55-12.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/the-jungle-book-et00040648-08-10-2016-03-55-12.jpg","d":"Directed by Jon Favreau, based on Rudyard Kipling's timeless stories and inspired by Disney's classic animated film, The Jungle Book is an all-new live-action epic adventure about Mowgli, a man-cub who has been raised by a family of wolves. <br/><br/>But Mowgli finds he is no longer welcome in the jungle when fearsome tiger Shere Khan, who bears the scars of Man, promises to eliminate what he sees as a threat. Urged to abandon the only home he has ever known, Mowgli embarks on a captivating journey of self-discovery, guided by panther-turned-stern mentor Bagheera, and the free-spirited bear Baloo. Along the way, Mowgli encounters jungle creatures who don't exactly have his best interests at heart, including Kaa, a python whose seductive voice and gaze hypnotizes the man-cub, and the smooth-talking King Louie, who tries to coerce Mowgli into giving up the secret to the elusive and deadly red flower: fire. <br/><br/>The Jungle Book seamlessly blends live-action with photorealistic CGI animals and environments, using up-to-the-minute technology and storytelling techniques to immerse audiences in an enchanting and lush world.","rd":"2016-04-08","rt":106,"ct":"UA","g":["Adventure","Drama","Fantasy"],"l":["English","Hindi","Tamil","Telugu"],"f":["2D","3D","IMAX 3D","4DX"],"i":null,"cast":[["Neel Sethi","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/neel-sethi-1059308-24-03-2017-16-19-36.jpg"],["Ben Kingsley","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/ben-kingsley-297-24-03-2017-12-42-17.jpg"],["Bill Murray","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/bill-murray-324-24-03-2017-12-37-08.jpg"],["Idri