{"ec":"ET00036069","t":"Theri","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/theri-et00036069-18-06-2017-01-41-22.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/theri-et00036069-18-06-2017-01-41-22.jpg","d":"A former police officer living under a new identity to protect his daughter is forced to confront his violent past when old enemies resurface. As threats to his family escalate, he must embrace his former self and seek justice, turning his fight into a relentless battle to protect his loved ones and uphold the law.","rd":"2016-04-14","rt":158,"ct":"U","g":["Action","Drama","Thriller"],"l":["Tamil"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Vijay","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/vijay-2461-20-12-2017-04-37-08.jpg"],["Amy Jackson","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/amy-jackson-18307-16-10-2018-12-26-15.jpg"],["Samantha Ruth Prabhu","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/samantha-ruth-prabhu-36761-1680672597.jpg"],["Raadhika Sarathkumar","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/raadhika-sarathkumar-1051035-05-04-2018-01-04-41.jpg"],["Prabhu","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/prabhu-1709-1747049366.jpg"],["J. Mahendran","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/j.-mahendran-1068664-24-03-2017-17-34-55.jpg"],["Nainika Vidyasagar","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/nainika-vidyasagar-1068089-24-03-2017-17-19-42.jpg"],["Kaali Venkat","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/kaali-venkat-1046320-1725444519.jpg"],["Stun Siva","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/stun-siva-iein050691-15-05-2018-15-13-40.jpg"]],"crew":{"d":[["Atlee","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/atlee-37797-1775638314.jpg"]]