{"ec":"ET00025074","t":"Fan","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/fan-et00025074-13-04-2018-09-47-25.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/fan-et00025074-13-04-2018-09-47-25.jpg","d":"Gaurav is a young man whose life revolves around his idol, the biggest movie star in the country. Determined to meet his hero, he travels to Mumbai believing his devotion will bring him closer to the man he worships. But when his dream encounter takes an unexpected turn, admiration slowly transforms into obsession, setting off a dangerous chain of events. As the lines between fan and superstar begin to blur, both men are forced to confront the consequences of fame, identity, and obsession.","rd":"2016-04-15","rt":145,"ct":"UA","g":["Drama","Thriller"],"l":["Hindi"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Shah Rukh Khan","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/shah-rukh-khan-2092-12-09-2017-02-10-43.jpg"],["Waluscha De Sousa","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/waluscha-de-sousa-1065106-24-03-2017-17-38-46.jpg"],["Shriya Pilgaonkar","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/shriya-pilgaonkar-36825-24-03-2017-17-57-33.jpg"],["Deepika Amin","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/deepika-amin-15908-06-12-2018-04-59-39.jpg"],["Yogendra Tiku","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/yogendra-tiku-1065512-10-04-2017-15-36-49.jpg"],["Sayani Gupta","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/sayani-gupta-29115-24-03-2017-16-00-55.jpg"],["Harbhajan Mann","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/harbhajan-mann-789-1697192077.jpg"]],"crew":{"d":[["Maneesh Sharma","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/maneesh-sharma-19857-24-03-2017-17-36-45.jpg"]],"p":[],"m":[["Vishal - Shekhar","https://a