{"ec":"ET00047996","t":"Biwi.com","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/biwicom-et00047996-04-01-2021-08-10-59.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/biwicom-et00047996-04-01-2021-08-10-59.jpg","d":"The film begins with the hero Kishan falling in love with a girl called Shilpa. They both visits a pandit who says that Karan will marry thrice in this life time. Shilpa gets upset with the pandit but he remains stubborn to his words. <br/><br/>Finally Shilpa and Kishan get married but soon, due to some circumstances, Shilpa forces Kishan for a second marriage. Later when the situation is sorted, Shilpa is not able to tolerate the second wife. It gets very difficult for Kishan to handle both the wives and in jest, Kishan says if they continue fighting like this, he will get a third wife. <br/><br/>And suddenly, the third wife from London comes back. To see what happens in Kishan`s life wait to watch Biwi.com","rd":"2016-10-21","rt":126,"ct":"UA","g":["Comedy","Romantic"],"l":["Hindi"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Karan Khanna","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/karan-khanna-1149-26-11-2019-11-42-14.jpg"],["Avani Modi","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/avani-modi-34204-1657190146.jpg"],["Priyanka Shah","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/priyanka-shah-27463-24-03-2017-16-00-15.jpg"],["Farah Titina","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/farah-titina-1075309-25-10-2018-10-43-35.jpg"],["Lekha Prajapati","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/lekha-prajapati-1053323-30-09-2020-03-14-13.jpg"]],"crew":{"d":[["Hanif Chhipa","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/hanif-chhipa-1075310-1674208080.jpg"]],"p":[],"m":[],"c":[],"e":[]}}
